      <title>美国进口税超过50％，可能会“破坏”加拿大木材</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/us-import-taxes-of-more-than-50-may-ravage-canadian-lumber</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国威胁要对加拿大木材产品的进口税，总计52％，这引起了对行业未来的担忧，并增加了美国房屋建设成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/us-import-taxes-of-more-than-50-may-ravage-canadian-lumber</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 23:10:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股票随着关税而降低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）承诺在数小时内向贸易伙伴征收关税，因此亚洲股将下跌，这使美国股票陷入了今年的最大损失，并提高了一场贸易战的幽灵，造成了全球经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 22:46:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本小型股基金最高的竞争对手有股票的分析师覆盖范围很少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/small-fund-beats-peers-with-japan-stocks-few-analysts-cover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本在合并和收购方面的持续繁荣正在帮助今年为一家小型基金带来优质回报，该基金重点关注股权分析师很少覆盖的公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/small-fund-beats-peers-with-japan-stocks-few-analysts-cover</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 22:37:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>B. Riley发布持续运营损失，收购工作结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/b-riley-posts-continuing-operations-loss-buyout-effort-ends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[B. Riley Financial Inc.在经纪和投资公司试图从酸味的投资中反弹，因此持续运营赢得了第四季度的初步损失。]]></description>
