    <item>
      <title>法国阿特斯（Altice France）的不愉快债权人提高顾问以提高条款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/altice-france-s-unhappy-creditors-tap-advisers-to-improve-terms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们说，一群对公司与大多数债权人之间安排的交易不满意的有担保债权人，削减约86亿欧元（90亿美元）的债务，使顾问聘请了顾问来找到提高其条款的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/altice-france-s-unhappy-creditors-tap-advisers-to-improve-terms</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 22:24:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>NVIDIA支持的IPO的CoreWeave文件显示出越来越多的收入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/nvidia-backed-coreweave-files-for-ipo-revealing-growing-revenue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CoreWeave是一家由云计算的提供商，是人工智能中最热门的初创公司之一，它申请了首次公开发行，披露了迅速增长的收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/nvidia-backed-coreweave-files-for-ipo-revealing-growing-revenue</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 22:13:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税的货币目标是征收税款迫在眉睫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/canada-mexico-currencies-drop-as-trump-confirms-looming-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从周二开始，唐纳德·特朗普总统确认对两国产品的产品启动了25％的产品，这是政府在一系列贸易公告中启动了25％的关税，这是政府在每日耗资7.5万美元的日常外国股票市场上为投资者提供自助式投资者的最新贸易公告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/canada-mexico-currencies-drop-as-trump-confirms-looming-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 20:21:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当食物进口气球时</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/trump-says-tariffs-on-agricultural-imports-to-start-april-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，美国将从4月2日开始对“外部”农产品征收关税，并增加了另一层威胁，以对进口商品施加贸易障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/trump-says-tariffs-on-agricultural-imports-to-start-april-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 18:41:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普中国关税面临的亚洲货币面临增长的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/asian-currencies-face-renewed-headwinds-as-tariff-fears-escalate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）宣布对中国的新关税，遏制他的威胁主要是讨价还价的策略之后，新兴亚洲货币的前景再次恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/asian-currencies-face-renewed-headwinds-as-tariff-fears-escalate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 08:32:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>S＆amp; p 500看到2025年最坏的抛售是债券的攀登：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[更加温和的经济新闻和唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的保证，要求对顶级贸易伙伴的关税强调，强调了华尔街的风险承受能力，将债券和股票寄给了一年中最大的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 22:43:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
